# Value SSOT Enforcement Rule

**Applies to:** `lib/domain/mizan-mantik/**`, `lib/domain/funnel-kernel/**`, orchestrator.ts, runner.ts, lib/oci/**

**Import ban:** `lib/utils/mizan-mantik.ts`, `lib/valuation/predictive-engine.ts`, `lib/domain/mizan-mantik/value-calculator.ts`, `lib/domain/funnel-kernel/funnel-policy.ts`.
Use `lib/oci/optimization-contract.ts` as the only optimization math authority.

## Golden Rules (Anayasa)

| Kural | Tanım | Teknik Karşılık |
|-------|-------|-----------------|
| **A** Single Math Authority | Optimization değeri başka yerde hesaplanmaz | `lib/oci/optimization-contract.ts` |
| **B** Single Stage Set | Sadece `junk`, `gorusuldu`, `teklif`, `satis` kullanılır | legacy V-stage alias yasak |
| **C** Single Writer | Snapshot kolonları tek canonical sözleşmeden dolar | `buildOptimizationSnapshot(...)` |
| **D** Integer Boundary | Cents sadece DB/export sınırında türetilir | `toExpectedValueCents`, queue guards |
| **E** Operational Config Only | Site config matematiği etkilemez | export/channel config serbest, value math değil |

## AI / Geliştirici Kuralları

- DO NOT read `sites.intent_weights`, `sites.default_aov`, or `oci_config.base_value` to shape optimization value.
- DO NOT reintroduce V-stage aliases (`V3_ENGAGE`, `V4_INTENT`, `V5_SEAL`, etc.) in active runtime code.
- ALWAYS derive optimization snapshots from `buildOptimizationSnapshot(...)`.
- ALWAYS perform cents conversion at the boundary, not inside stage math.
- For any value mismatch in sync tasks, log `QUEUE_VALUE_MISMATCH` instead of overwriting.

## Integer Cents Detay

- Internal SSOT: `optimization_value` major units, `expected_value_cents` / `value_cents` boundary fields.
- Örnek doğru: `const snapshot = buildOptimizationSnapshot({ stage, systemScore })`
- Yasak: `default_aov * ratio`, `intent_weights[...]`, `decay(...)` ile optimization value üretmek
